resources.string: *How do I pay for the items that I borrow?

A mobile application for renting the resources for increase sustainability. As we know we have a lot of things in our home that we are not using in our day-to-day life, so instead of keeping them for long use without operating we can rent those resources in our local people or community to increase the productivity and sustainability.

*How many ads can I post in RentME?
There are no limits to how many ADS users can post as long as it is unique. Duplicates are rejected by the Admin.
*How long do Ads stay on RentME?
Ad duration is not specified unless it is unavailable or removed by user themselves.
